      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-032</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 32.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 32.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>始制有名，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>As soon as it proceeds to action, it has a name.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-032__align-006">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-032</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 32.10 - 老子 32.12</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 32.6 - 老子 32.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>名亦既有，夫亦將知止，知止所以不殆。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When it once has that name, (men) can know to rest in it. When they know to rest in it, they can be free from all risk of failure and error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
